item.description:
@Helro wrote:

http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp

follow these instructions:

  1. click on the following link i gave u
  2. When the site showes up click on the download button next to “JDK 6u1”
  3. now click “accept” (below is a picture on how it looks like)

Required: You must accept the license agreement to download the product.

Accept License Agreement | Review License Agreement <<— click this one!
Decline License Agreement

  1. Wait for it to refresh the page
  2. put a tick on the “Windows Offline Installation, Multi-language”
    DO NOT CLICK “download selected with sun download manager”
  3. click on “Windows Offline Installation, Multi-language” just click on it!

follow what it says and there u go that should help u!
